		<h2>Styling</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Navigation bar lists the main views. Lesser used screens are available under Others</li>
			<li>Hyper-linked entities are shown in bold green, and will display the entity's detail page</li>
			<li>Action buttons are in dark green, and are clustered in the top section in both index and display pages</li> 
