			<li>Search screens with many entries provide drop downs and a wildcard search option</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Member</h2>
		All participants are defined as members with manager, title and stream. There is no authentication or feature for "current user". Member details screen is the GOTO screen for each architect. 
		<ul>
			<li><b>Topics:</b> Members can bookmark topics of interest, so they are readily available for reference</li>
			<li><b>Course Submission:</b> Members can recommend new courses as part of the Discovery phase</li>
			<li><b>Team:</b> Members can join teams for discovery or training groups</li>
			<li><b>Subscription:</b> Members can select the courses they plan to undertake. They can update training status, and also rate the course and add review comments on completion</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Team</h2>
		Teams can be formed for discovery, training and demonstration. Discovery teams are named by leader. Learning group teams might more appropriately be named by Topic. 
